It works flawlessly! Here&#x27;s a helper function for chatting which includes your handle before each message (helps keep track of who&#x27;s saying what):<p><pre><code>  KBUSER=`keybase status | grep Username | awk &#x27;{print $NF}&#x27;`;
  function say() { echo &quot;$KBUSER: $@&quot; >> /keybase/private/shared,folder,between,multiple,users/chat.txt }
</code></pre>
Note: I made KBUSER a variable because `keybase status` takes about a second to run.
